Author: bandar
Title: [ANN][ICO] «froshfeel - froins» Decentralized Student Network
Body: I like the idea of a network focused on everything related to students/learning/the academic world.  I see you propose some user cases.  Froins should be the tokens (coins) that would be used by students & everybody around the academic world.  Can you elaborate on why they would use froins and not some major cryptocurrency like eth?  Are there, in other words, specific benefits for using this coin?  Another question: are there contacts with the academic world yet?  Are there universities/academic institutions who are interested or aboard?

Author: froshfeel | froins
Title: [ANN][ICO] «froshfeel - froins» Decentralized Student Network
Body: Hi Bandar,  Yes, the users are provided incentives by using froins. There is a point system, which determines certain benefits to the user. The more froins spent, the higher the points, the bigger the discounts and deals they will be able to redeem on the froshfeel platform. In other words, the user will receive discounts and deals by using froins, which they would not receive by using any other cryptocurrency or fiat cash.  Yes, we have already been in contact with associations that institutes belong to. We have had positive feedback from multiple associations who are very welcoming to a platform such as froshfeel to assist student's as they journey through their educational experience.
